 <h1 style="color:blue";>About</h1>
    <p>Music lessons are a type of formal instruction in playing a musical instrument or singing.
Typically, a student taking music lessons meets a music teacher for one-on-one training sessions ranging from 30 minutes to one hour in length over a period of weeks or years.
Depending on lessons to be taught, students learn different skills relevant to the instruments used.
Music teachers also assign technical exercises, musical pieces, and other activities to help the students improve their musical skil</p>
  </section>
