    <h1 style="color:blue";>online classes</h1>
<p>We are the best Carnatic Classical Music Academy in Hyderabad, specialized in both online music classes and
offline music classes, established in the year 1998 with an aim to spread the knowledge of CARNATIC MUSIC worldwide.
We started with a single branch in Hyderabad and expanded our wings to various branches across Hyderabad, Bangalore, Vizianagaram and Tirupati.
We take the privilege of holding First Online Music Classes since 2008 and have a Very Ambitious and Highly Qualified Music Teachers who can withhold
and drive the passion of the students by training them in different modes of music like light music/kritis or kirtanas during the
regular Carnatic Music Lessons to drive and sustain their interest in their passion.</p>
